##Isolation (1)

Vicechina  

Function description, different color vision

Editor's Note: The author of this article is our previous, this story, the protagonist, the media person Jia Qiu. He is still in quarantine period, two days ago a little cold and fever, fortunately is false alarm. What is it like to be a potential "virus contactee" who reports to the authorities? We asked Rachel to write it down.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
A little over two weeks ago, out at sea in the Arctic Circle, the ice was freezing, the waves were choppy, and we were throwing up, and the captain said, "Life is hard, Life is always hard. "

At that time, we didn't know how bad the situation was thousands of miles away in our native land. We could still dance "the northernmost wolf Disco" on the roiling decks of the frozen world to combat the pervasive cold of the Arctic Circle, to Comfort each other while we still have time for kindness.

That is, until a message quietly popped up on my screen, changing the tone of the images for the next few days:

On the second day of my return to China, I boarded the train heading south and joined the huge freight train that had set off from Changzhou via Hefei in the middle of the night. I "escorted" the whole bus of the donated atomized medical supplies to Hubei, stopping first in Wuhan and then in Jingzhou to turn back to Moshen Mountain, back to the Riverside Warehouse, until the last batch of donated medical supplies unloaded. To avoid infection, we did not choose to stay overnight, drove out of Hubei overnight, each home, the initiative reported, and then formally activated isolation.

Turn off your cell phone, which is still silent. At the moment, the window is still a white, but with two weeks ago to see the Arctic circle is completely different from the cold silence.

A Faint Murmur of conversation could be heard through the windows, and the rustle of a nearby neighbor's cough would suddenly cease, as if all ears in a building were pricked up to make sure they were not voices.

All images courtesy of the author

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
I leaned against the window and looked at the snow left by Beijing a few days ago. The car downstairs or whatever it was, it was almost completely covered in snow, untouched. After looking down on the land of China for a long time, I finally counted the number of footprints on the roof of the car, all from the cat walking sideways.

On the fifth day of isolation, apart from being more strict with yourself and being in bed for as long as 12 hours or more each day, you are alone and enjoy the silence with a kind of familiarity.

Clothes to hand, not to mouth to barely be a meal. As I returned from the epidemic area is the focus of the distribution control object, and is the initiative to report, the neighborhood aunt's enthusiasm at least seems to be very strong. However, segregation, giving money, free food and so on are just legends.

Open your alcohol-washed mobile phone and connect to the only "royalty" serving vegetables in the grocery store "Jin Gong" -- Foshan -- and check the "royal priced" vegetables without bargaining, only a discussion of what kind of turnip it is. After that, the princess will personally deliver it to my door, quietly.

Unlike the two security men who come to the door every day at 2 p.m. to help me pick up the garbage, each time they go out of their way to disinfect the door with a loud voice and a full set of 84 sanitizers, in case the neighbors didn't know, there was something unusual about this house.

The Neighborhood Committee comrade for the convenience I buy food, at first only gave a Qr code, scan found that only payment

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
When I finally got in touch with Princess Jian, I was able to buy groceries. Princess Jin will confirm the payment after I receive the goods

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Sometimes food and garbage arrive at the door at the same time

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Neighborhood Committee comrades and I are encrypted daily, the basic number of chat, 36.3,36.4,36.5, but not to 36.8. He called me at eight in the morning to wake me up for his daily temperature report, which was on time in the morning and at night. Apparently, meticulous, meticulous, has been internalized in the grass-roots civil servants for many years adhere to the principle of self-discipline. But if the system had worked more efficiently, things might be different today.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In order to enrich the isolation life, I just ordered a case of drinks on the Internet, apparently they are very heavy, I had to tentatively ask the neighborhood comrades. This time my small heart, he did not hesitate to answer one mouthful. It appears that care is genuine and routine, within the limits of clear authority. The community currently requires that deliveries and takeout be stopped at the gate, that free people can go to the border to trade, and that sequestered people like me only have to wait for the security guard to help me with the last kilometer of this express replenishment service.

In fact, even in bed, the degree of busyness is not lower than usual. I am leading an observer mission, the first task of which is to monitor the implementation of the tasks that led to my isolation five days ago. In recent days, everyone is following the round-the-clock shifts ahead, including Red Cross staff, a remote tracking of the transfer of supplies and hospital usage. And the folks on the ground with the cameras, and the creators and volunteers all over the world, need to support each other closely.

With jet LAG and two nights in a row in the front seat of a van, I would love to stay in bed 12 hours longer than I have in the past few days. It was always felt that the outbreak might actually change the way many people think about work and life, such as the feasibility of long distance work and study without having to be specifically verified. This reminds me of a little sister whom my friends asked me to donate and take care of regularly on the outskirts of Deyang after the Sichuan Earthquake:

Little sister sensible clever, unfortunately suffering from muscle weakness. To the third grade, the head teacher also can not continue to carry can not walk the little sister to school. There's no cure for Myasthenia Gravis, and it's getting worse. A few friends in Hebei finally chose to donate a computer. Little sister later became a gold medal Taobao customer service. Every time I went, she sat on the bed with a steady smile after her busy work, not only because she found a sustainable work direction, and because she found her place in the new world of relationships. Obviously, the virtual economy is not the monster of the flood. This time, we do not intend to make money for the national calamity. Add, call her little sister, besides feel alias ice-cold, also because of her home, also can not walk muscle weakness sister.

The splendid Tianfu Pagoda in Chengdu, Sichuan, cheers for Wuhan

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
As long as the human heart is not on an island, we have a chance to return to civilization. Remember, to the discovery of oil in northern European fishermen, who had to boil out the sentence millennium chicken soup: Life is always bitter. How do we deal with it?

The shipment to Jingzhou also brought me into contact with a reclusive pen pal -- an old man selling vegetables. Not by chance, his provincial daughter-in-law is my little sister-in-law. It was the first time for Yan er, a newly married woman, to return to Jingzhou from Changsha with her husband for the New Year. Being able to work remotely, she was stuck in the village with nothing to worry about but an unsettled family situation.

This place used to be full of radishes. Maybe Princess Jin was out of stock

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In an epidemic, everyone is in danger. Only the restless father-in-law, from the second day of the Lunar New Year to the fourth day of the Lunar New Year, every month high in the dark, drove his beloved minivan, carrying affordable vegetables, from no-man's lane across the blockade to touch the city of Jingzhou. The price of the vegetables in the city could have risen fivefold, but the old man was only thinking of his promise to his patrons to deliver them on time, without raising their prices. The mother-in-law led her relatives in full persuasion in the family group because of the irregular adventure plan. In the end, the public turned away in anger.

The old man's car

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
But like the bickering family, the old man who had doggedly completed his top secret mission locked himself away in his room as soon as he got home.

"The two pots from the father self-isolation, is his special pot, " said little sister

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Although they are in the same yard with their families, they have no close contact with them. They wash their clothes alone and dry them separately. When they are cooking alone, they naturally have to take them back to their small rooms to eat because of their limited cooking skills, cooking noodles with pickles is the first hot dish on the isolation menu.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
And the ingredients, like the eggs on this table and the Artemisia stalks on the floor, are all from friends. These so-called friends are the regular customers of the vegetable supply and marketing cooperative. The world will return the favor. We must seize the day.

As a few days prior to my isolation, the old gentleman just half of the schedule, already not satisfied with the living room. So, the impatient old man sneaked back to the family group, made a little observation, and threw out a wechat article, "urgent! Please let the "vegetable basket" pass! They need help. " Then added a sentence, "logging tired of the family hello! Today I insomnia, looked at the phone calendar, today first to the group of all people send the New Year's greetings late! "

No one replied, the old man then said: "This year's Spring Festival is the most memorable we have, but also the most test of the people's hearts. ". Why do you say that? This year's Spring Festival outbreak of a new coronavirus, the country launched a first-level response. We should all respond to the party's call and follow its instructions. But instead I went out, bringing panic and risk to my family, turning what should have been a happy Spring Festival into a battlefield, hurting all my closest relatives, making you worry about me, I am deeply sorry, I was wrong, please understand!"

It is estimated that the draft has been prepared early, the old man did not wait for the reaction to say: "Today in the group of retweets about the cabbage son of a link, these are also I saw the closure of the city road and Related Epidemic News after the most worrying thing. ". I am a member of the vegetable growing community, and I know how hard they work. Since the fourth day of the seventh lunar month, I have received calls from order-growing farmers, as well as urgent orders from suppliers of supermarkets and prison canteens. I have not suffered any national calamity, and my conscience is clear!"

"during the Spring Festival, when the virus outbreak happens during the Spring Festival, the Chinese people have a good tradition. Every family has enough supplies for life. We can live at home for as little as a week or as long as a month without purchasing, so we can reduce panic and worry. It's a national blessing. So the question is, the younger generation in the group, you are all the future of the country, you are all college students, if you don't have the life reserves in your home for two days, who will be the retrograde one?"

Reading this, I suddenly felt that my remote isolation predecessor, much like a man.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Yes, The Fantastic Mr. Fox!

Perhaps before the catastrophe, everything is still time to be treated kindly; and the ordinary isolator, is also the most can not forget the quack.

That's enough emotion.

Empty talk occasionally solves the problem, empty talk mostly misguides the country.

Quarantine one, over.
